::DarkMouse::

She looked around.  She noticed that she hadn't seen Scorponok in the 
main cave lately.  She wondered if he was in his lab working on 
something important.  "Pardon me commander, I'll be right back."
She walked over to Scorponok's lab.  She didn't see him there.  She 
walked inside and looked around.  She saw tools and other things 
laying about. "I'm going to have to have him pick up his toys more 
often." she chuckled to herself.  She saw a black box sitting on the 
work bench.  She wondered what it was.  She picked it up and looked 
at it.  It didn't open and she couldn't find the open button.  She 
set it down and walked back out to the entrance of the cave.
"Uh, Commander Quickstrike, if you happen to see Scorponok, let him 
know that i am loking for him."

She turned and went back to her computer console.
